
'''= OpenRide is an innovative software application for arranging spontaneous ride sharing via smartphone. OpenRide saves you money, helps protect the environment and improves individual mobility!'''

URL = http://www.open-ride.com/en.html


=Description=

"OpenRide is as open source software under the Affero Gnu public license (AGPL v3) on Sourceforge freely available and expandable. On the basis of OpenRide, anyone can realise their own mobility ideas: Develop new functionalities for drivers and passengers. Expand the system with innovative mobility services. Use OpenRide to build and operate your own shared-ride community or integrate OpenRide into your community software."


